Package zuul.gameState.maps

Class ZuulMap

java.lang.Object
zuul.gameState.maps.Map
zuul.gameState.maps.ZuulMap
public class ZuulMap
extends Map
World of Zuul standard Map.

This map has five Rooms (outside, theatre, pub, lab, and office) and one Player (player1)

Character "player1" starts in the room "outside".

Room "outside" contains a single item "notebook".

    • printWelcome

      public void printWelcome()
      Description copied from class: Map
      Prints a welcome message to the player.

      This should be called at the start of the game flow logic.

      This method should introduce the player to this Map.

      It is recommended that a prompt to type the 'help' command be printed in this method.
